[[File:SalthiaBean.jpg|200px|thumb|A bowl of salthia beans]]
'''Salthia beans''' were used to make a nutritious paste for the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Navy]].

The well known bean could be foraged on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]] and added to other [[Foodstuff/Legends|foods]] to enhance their nutritional value.<ref name="AED">{{GalaxiesAED}}</ref>

The beans were often fed to [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo's]] children when they were infants on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], occasionally being used in their food fights.<ref name="TCSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>

